race.description: Watsons Caravans Port Macquarie Showcase Handicap (C2)
race.comment: SOSUEME (9) got off the mark with an impressive maiden win last time out over 1106m at this track. Serious contender again with the confidence high. SEND A TELEGRAM (7) pushed forward when resuming last time and boxed on to finish third over 1000m at Coffs Harbour. Well placed and there is no reason he cannot salute. SPARKINGLY (5) found the line strongly last time when third at Taree. Suited at the longer journey and is among the winning hopes. SHEILA'S FANTA SEA (10) has been leaving herself with too much to do but warming nicely late. If she settle a pair or two closer, she will take some stopping. OUTAKANDY (1) returns and gets help under the big weight with the claim. Best of the rest.
